# PraisonAI рҹҰһ

<a href="https://trendshift.io/repositories/9130" target="_blank"><img src="https://trendshift.io/api/badge/repositories/9130" alt="MervinPraison%2FPraisonAI | Trendshift" style="width: 250px; height: 55px;" width="250" height="55"/></a>

</div>

PraisonAI рҹҰһ вҖ” **Hire a 24/7 AI Workforce.** Stop writing boilerplate and start shipping autonomous, self-improving agents that research, plan, and execute tasks across your apps. From one agent to an entire organization, deployed in 5 lines of code.

```bash
curl -fsSL https://praison.ai/install.sh | bash
```

