## рҹҢҹ Why PraisonAI?

| | Feature | How |
|--|---------|-----|
| рҹ”Ң | **MCP Protocol** вҖ” stdio, HTTP, WebSocket, SSE | `tools=MCP("npx ...")` |
| рҹ§  | **Planning Mode** вҖ” plan вҶ’ execute вҶ’ reason | `planning=True` |
| рҹ”Қ | **Deep Research** вҖ” multi-step autonomous research | [Docs](https://docs.praison.ai/docs/agents/deep-research) |
| рҹӨ– | **External Agents** вҖ” orchestrate Claude Code, Gemini CLI, Codex | [Docs](https://docs.praison.ai/docs/code/external-agents) |
| рҹ”„ | **Agent Handoffs** вҖ” seamless conversation passing | `handoff=True` |
| рҹӣЎпёҸ | **Guardrails** вҖ” input/output validation | [Docs](https://docs.praison.ai/docs/concepts/guardrails) |
|  | **Web Search + Fetch** вҖ” native browsing | `web_search=True` |
| рҹӘһ | **Self Reflection** вҖ” agent reviews its own output | [Docs](https://docs.praison.ai/docs/concepts/reflection) |
| рҹ”Җ | **Workflow Patterns** вҖ” route, parallel, loop, repeat | [Docs](https://docs.praison.ai/docs/concepts/agentflow) |
| рҹ§  | **Memory (zero deps)** вҖ” works out of the box | `memory=True` |

