## вҡЎ Performance

PraisonAI is built for speed, with agent instantiation in around 14Ојs. This reduces overhead, improves responsiveness, and helps multi-agent systems scale efficiently in real-world production workloads.

| Performance Metric | PraisonAI |
|--------------------|-----------|
| Avg Instantiation Time | **14 Ојs** |

